data.description: Welcome to this spacious and well-maintained 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom, 2-story home with a 2-car garage and a basement, perfectly situated in a highly desirable neighborhood with an excellent school district. This home offers the ideal blend of comfort, style, and convenience, making it the perfect place for you and your family to create lasting memories. This home provides ample space for your family and guests, offering five generously-sized bedrooms that can be used for sleeping, office space, or hobbies. With three well-appointed bathrooms, mornings are a breeze, and everyone can get ready without any hassle.Protect your vehicles from the elements in the spacious two-car garage. Plus, there's ample driveway space for additional parking. The two-story layout provides separation between the living and sleeping areas, ensuring privacy and a sense of spaciousness. The basement is a versatile space that can be customized to your liking. Use it as a recreation room, home gym, or additional storage. This home has been meticulously cared for, so you can move in with confidence, knowing it's in excellent condition. Enjoy the convenience of being close to shopping, restaurants, and entertainment options, making errands and leisure activities a breeze. The kitchen is equipped with updated appliances and plenty of counter space, perfect for preparing delicious meals. The living room features a charming fireplace, providing warmth and ambiance during chilly evenings. Large windows throughout the home let in an abundance of natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. This home is a fantastic opportunity to live in a sought-after neighborhood while enjoying all the space and features you need. Don't miss out on the chance to make this house your home.
